            <div id="sm-cog-elements" class="noprint"></div>
            <div class="allset-page-heading"><h1>Two words for "but"</h1></div>
            <!-- subtitle -->
            <div id="contentSub" ><span class="mw-redirectedfrom">(Redirected from <a href="https://resources.allsetlearning.com/gramwiki/?title=ASGUD81S&amp;redirect=no" class="mw-redirect" title="ASGUD81S">ASGUD81S</a>)</span></div>
            <!-- /subtitle -->
                        <div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="mw-parser-output"><div id="ibox" class="toc">
	<div class="ibox-link"><span class="plainlinks"><a href="ASGUD81S" class="mw-redirect" title="ASGUD81S"><img src="https&#58;//resources.allsetlearning.com/gramwiki/images/silk/link.png" /></a></span></div>
	<ul class="ibox-list">
               <li class="ibox-level-cefr-hsk clearfix">
                        
			<div class="ibox-label">Level</div>
			<div class="ibox-info"><span style="font-size: 1.4em;"><a href="A2_grammar_points" title="A2 grammar points"> A2</a></span> / <span style="font-size:0.75em;"><a href="HSK4_grammar_points" class="mw-redirect" title="HSK4 grammar points">HSK4</a></span></div>
		</li>
		<li class="ibox-level clearfix" style="display:none">
			<div class="ibox-label">Level</div>
			<div class="ibox-info"><a href="A2_grammar_points" title="A2 grammar points"> A2</a></div>
		</li>
		<li class="ibox-level-hsk clearfix" style="display:none;">
			<div class="ibox-label">Level</div>
			<div class="ibox-info"><a href="HSK4_grammar_points" class="mw-redirect" title="HSK4 grammar points"> HSK4</a></div>
		</li>
		<li class="ibox-similarto clearfix">
			<div class="ibox-label">Similar to</div>
			<div class="ibox-info"><ul class="smw-format ul-format"><li class="smw-row"><span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value"><a href="A_softer_&quot;but&quot;_with_&quot;buguo&quot;" title="A softer &quot;but&quot; with &quot;buguo&quot;">A softer "but" with "buguo"</a></span></span> (<span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value">B1</span></span>)</li><li class="smw-row"><span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value"><a href="Expressing_&quot;although&quot;_with_&quot;suiran&quot;_and_&quot;danshi&quot;" title="Expressing &quot;although&quot; with &quot;suiran&quot; and &quot;danshi&quot;">Expressing "although" with "suiran" and "danshi"</a></span></span> (<span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value">B1</span></span>)</li></ul></div>
		</li>
		<li class="ibox-similarto-hsk clearfix" style="display:none;">
			<div class="ibox-label">Similar to</div>
			<div class="ibox-info"><ul class="smw-format ul-format"><li class="smw-row"><span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value"><a href="Expressing_&quot;although&quot;_with_&quot;suiran&quot;_and_&quot;danshi&quot;" title="Expressing &quot;although&quot; with &quot;suiran&quot; and &quot;danshi&quot;">Expressing "although" with "suiran" and "danshi"</a></span></span> (<span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value">HSK2</span></span>)</li><li class="smw-row"><span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value"><a href="A_softer_&quot;but&quot;_with_&quot;buguo&quot;" title="A softer &quot;but&quot; with &quot;buguo&quot;">A softer "but" with "buguo"</a></span></span> (<span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value">HSK4</span></span>)</li></ul></div>
		</li>
		<li class="ibox-usedfor clearfix">
			<div class="ibox-label">Used for</div>
			<div class="ibox-info"><a href="Contrasting" title="Contrasting">Contrasting</a>, <a href="Connecting_ideas" title="Connecting ideas">Connecting ideas</a> </div>
		</li>
		<li class="ibox-keywords clearfix">
			<div class="ibox-label">Keywords</div>
			<div class="ibox-info"><a href="可" title="可">可</a>, <a href="但是" title="但是">但是</a>, <a href="可是" title="可是">可是</a>, <a href="但" title="但">但</a></div>
		</li>
		
	</ul>
	<div class="ibox-image"><a href="./File:Chinese-grammar-wiki-ke.jpg" class="image"><img alt="Chinese-grammar-wiki-ke.jpg" src="https://resources.allsetlearning.com/gramwiki/images/thumb/9/97/Chinese-grammar-wiki-ke.jpg/300px-Chinese-grammar-wiki-ke.jpg" decoding="async" width="300" height="300" srcset="https://resources.allsetlearning.com/gramwiki/images/thumb/9/97/Chinese-grammar-wiki-ke.jpg/450px-Chinese-grammar-wiki-ke.jpg 1.5x, https://resources.allsetlearning.com/gramwiki/images/thumb/9/97/Chinese-grammar-wiki-ke.jpg/600px-Chinese-grammar-wiki-ke.jpg 2x" /></a></div>
</div> 
<p>Using "but" in Chinese is really simple to learn. It involves the two words 可是 (kěshì) and 但是 (dànshì). Make no "buts" about it; you'll understand it in no time!
</p>
<div id="toc" class="toc"><input type="checkbox" role="button" id="toctogglecheckbox" class="toctogglecheckbox" style="display:none" /><div class="toctitle" lang="en" dir="ltr"><h2>Contents</h2><span class="toctogglespan"><label class="toctogglelabel" for="toctogglecheckbox"></label></span></div>
<ul>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-1"><a href="ASGUD81S#Structure"><span class="tocnumber">1</span> <span class="toctext">Structure</span></a></li>
